videos.description: TCU's Alex Robinson comes up with the steal and makes the layup after being fouled on the other end against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: TCU continues early domination over Georgia Tech with and-1

videos.description: Michael Williams finds Brandon Parrish inside for the easy bucket as TCU extends their lead over Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to bucket for TCU

videos.description: Tadric Jackson and Josh Okogie throw down wide open dunks in consecutive possessions as Georgia Tech tries to get back in it against TCU.
videos.headline: Back-to-back dunks energize Yellow Jackets

videos.description: Alex Robinson finds Vladimir Brodziansky with the bounce pass as TCU continues their strong half against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: TCU carves up defense with the pick and roll

videos.description: Kenrich Williams drives baseline and finishes the two-handed dunk after being fouled to extend TCU's lead over Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: TCU dunk caps off impressive first half

videos.description: TCU's Kenrich Williams collects the rebound for the putback dunk against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: TCU putback slam brings bench to their feet

videos.description: TCU's Vladimir Brodziansky cleans up Kenrich Williams' miss for a putback dunk against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Botched alley-oop turns into ridiculous putback dunk

videos.description: Alex Robinson finds Desmond Bane in the corner for the 3-pointer as TCU continues to go all out against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: TCU putting on a show with ball movement  in NIT Final

videos.description: Alex Robinson finds Desmond Bane with the creative pass for the layup as TCU piles it on against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: TCU getting fancy in transition

videos.description: Josh Parrish seals the win for TCU with a huge dunk as they beat Georgia Tech to win the NIT.
videos.headline: TCU ends NIT with emphatic dunk

videos.description: TCU head coach, Jamie Dixon, talks about proving how good his team with an NIT title.
videos.headline: Dixon proud of his team after winning NIT

videos.description: TCU dominates Georgia Tech from the start to the finish to win the NIT championship 88-56.
videos.headline: TCU beats Georgia Tech in impressive fashion to take NIT title
